@page "/spreadsheet/overview"

@using Syncfusion.Blazor.Spreadsheet
@using System;
@using System.IO;

@*Hidden:Lines*@
@inherits SampleBaseComponent;
@inject Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.NavigationManager UriHelper
@*End:Hidden*@

<SampleDescription>
    <p>This overview sample demonstrates the core capabilities of the Blazor Spreadsheet component, offering a high-level view of its most essential features. It highlights how the component efficiently handles large datasets using virtual scrolling, while also showcasing key user interactions like formula editing, data entry, and cell formatting. This sample serves as a comprehensive introduction for users to explore the full potential of the Blazor Spreadsheet in real-world scenarios.</p>
</SampleDescription>
<ActionDescription>
    <p>In this sample, we have enabled <b>drag selection</b> for intuitive cell range selection, and implemented clipboard operations like <b>cut</b>, <b>copy</b>, and <b>paste</b> for seamless data manipulation. We have also included <b>column and row resizing</b> to support layout customization, and a <b>footer</b> to provide quick summary insights.</p>
    <p> Interactive <b>row and column headers</b> allow for easy bulk selection. The <b>formula bar</b> is fully functional with <b>syntax highlighting</b> and <b>autocomplete</b>, enhancing formula entry and editing. Additionally, the sample demonstrates support for <b>RTL mode</b> and <b>hyperlink interactions</b>, emphasizing accessibility and interactivity. These implementations offer a practical and complete glimpse into the component's versatility and responsiveness.</p>
    <p><b>Note:</b> The <code>AllowAutofill</code> property is set to <code>false</code> in this sample, so the autofill handle will not be displayed when selecting a cell.</p>
</ActionDescription>
<div class="col-lg-12 control-section">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="row">

            <div>
                <SfSpreadsheet DataSource="DataSourceBytes" AllowAutofill="false" AllowSorting="false">
                    <SpreadsheetRibbon></SpreadsheetRibbon>
                </SfSpreadsheet>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@*Hidden:Lines*@
<style>
    .e-spreadsheet-protection-dialog label,
    .e-spreadsheet-unprotect-dialog label,
    .e-unprotectworkbook-dlg label,
    .e-spreadsheet-name-manager-content label {
        font-weight: normal !important;
        margin-bottom: 0 !important;
    }

    .e-protectworkbook-dlg label {
        font-weight: normal !important;
    }
</style>
@*End:Hidden*@

@code {

    public byte[] DataSourceBytes { get; set; }

    protected override void OnInitialized()
    {
        @*Server:Block*@
#if !(WASM || WEBAPP)
        //Sets the excel file path for initial loading.
        string filePath = "wwwroot/data/spreadsheet/emi-spreadsheet.xlsx";
        DataSourceBytes = File.ReadAllBytes(filePath);
#endif
        @*End:Server*@

        @*WebAssembly:Block*@
#if (WASM || WEBAPP)
    //Sets the excel file path for initial loading.
    string filePath = "";
        DataSourceBytes = Convert.FromBase64String(filePath);
#endif
        @*End:WebAssembly*@
    }
}
